<div class="content-page">
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

  <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
  <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the website remember your preferences and understand how you use the site.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Cookies</h2>
  <p>LighterMe uses cookies only with your explicit consent. When you first visit our site, you'll see a cookie banner giving you the choice to accept or reject cookies. Both options are equally easy to select.</p>

  <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
  <p>These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be turned off. They include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cookie consent preference</strong> — remembers whether you accepted or rejected cookies (stored in your browser's local storage)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Analytics Cookies (Only If You Accept)</h3>
  <p>If you accept cookies, we may use analytics tools to understand how visitors use our site. These cookies help us:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>See which pages are most visited</li>
    <li>Understand how visitors navigate through the site</li>
    <li>Identify areas for improvement</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Affiliate Tracking Cookies</h3>
  <p>When you click an affiliate link on our site, the third-party clinic or network (such as Awin) may set a tracking cookie on your device. This cookie:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Tracks that you were referred by LighterMe</li>
    <li>Typically lasts 30 days</li>
    <li>Is set by the third party, not by us</li>
    <li>Allows us to earn a commission if you sign up for a programme</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We are not responsible for cookies set by third-party websites. Please refer to their cookie policies for more information.</p>

  <h2>Managing Your Cookies</h2>
  <p>You can manage cookies in several ways:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Our cookie banner:</strong> Accept or reject cookies when you first visit</li>
    <li><strong>Browser settings:</strong> Most browsers allow you to block or delete cookies via Settings → Privacy</li>
    <li><strong>Clear local storage:</strong> To reset your cookie preference on our site, clear your browser's local storage for lighterme.co.uk</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Under PECR (Privacy and Electronic Communications Regulations) and UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Choose whether to accept or reject cookies</li>
    <li>Change your preference at any time</li>
    <li>Browse our site without accepting cookies (essential functionality will still work)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about our use of cookies, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@lighterme.co.uk">hello@lighterme.co.uk</a>.</p>
</div>

